See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: cf walloper, universal; wolloper used in relation to kitchen work and to threshing.  Note US base ball use.
Citations
Date: 26/9/1884
Source: Hawke's Bay Herald
Author:
Vol / Page: 4
Edition:
Quote: One of the parties to the suit was at last called upon for an explanation, and he, with a look of contemptuous pity for those who had to confess such gross ignorance by enquiring, explained that "chaffy," "baggy," and "strawwolloper" were the respective names of artists who attended to the wants of a threshing machine.
