Author:
Vol / Page: 4
Edition:
Quote: The kitchen pot wolloper too, with her blue mottled elbows, was there in abundance, and rang out her dulcet notes of welcome on the morning zephers with as much enthusiasm as her more favored sister with the Sealskin ulster, more antique skirt, and pink complexion.
